e ...\"</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Commonwealth_of_World_Citizens&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/World_Service_Authority\" title=\"World Service Authority\">World Service Authority</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/World_Passport\" title=\"World Passport\">World Passport</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Commonwealth_of_World_Citizens&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: External links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>More information is available at:\n</p>\n<dl><dd><ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.mondcivitan.org\">The Mondcivitan Republic</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.schonfield.org\">The Hugh &amp; Helene Schonfield World Service Trust</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ilbs.org/\">International Leadership and Business Society</a></li></ul></dd></dl>\n<ul><li><cite class=\"citation book\">April Carter (4 July 2013). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://books.google.com/books?id=VS9f19oD1CkC&amp;pg=PT197\"><i>The Political Theory of Global Citizenship</i></a>. Routledge. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-1-134-70108-7\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-1-134-70108-7\">978-1-134-70108-7</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book